# Profinite Fenchel groups

Public entry point for the profinite Fenchel-Nielsen library.

The root module intentionally exposes only the narrowed public surface:

* profinite Fenchel group presentations and signature API;
* existence of torsion-free open normal/characteristic subgroups;
* the non-perfect three-step torsion-free open subgroup theorem.

Auxiliary quotient constructions and discrete transport modules remain available through their
specific files, but are not re-exported here.
